email-classification-api/
├── app.py                # Main app entry point
├── api.py                # API endpoints using FastAPI or Flask
├── models.py             # Model training and loading functions
├── utils.py              # PII masking/demasking and helper functions
├── data/                 # Provided dataset for training/testing
│   └── support_emails.csv
├── saved_models/         # Saved classification models and encoders
├── requirements.txt      # Python dependencies
├── README.md             # Setup and usage instructions
└── report.pdf            # Project report
